OL,3,CMPs demand Hillsborough Law is
OL,4,Cdelivered 'in full and without delay'
OL,6,FMore than 50 MPs from eight political
OL,7,Fparties have signed a parliamentary
OL,8,Fmotion urging the prime minister to
OL,9,Fdeliver on his promise to introduce
OL,10,Fthe so-called Hillsborough Law.
OL,12,FThe Early Day Motion, tabled by
OL,13,FLiverpool West Derby MP Ian Byrne ` a
OL,14,FHillsborough survivor and the
OL,15,Fparliamentary lead for the
OL,16,FHillsborough Law Now campaign `
OL,17,Fhighlights how the prime minister
OL,18,Ffailed to meet his own 15 April 2025
OL,19,Fdeadline to introduce the law. That
OL,20,Fdate marked the 36th anniversary of
OL,21,Fthe disaster.
