OL,6,FThe motion also raises "grave concern
OL,7,Fat reports that the Government intends
OL,8,Fto bring forward a weakened
OL,9,Falternative bill, lacking the core
OL,10,Fprinciples and protections of the
OL,11,FHillsborough Law."
OL,13,FBacked by cross-party support, the
OL,14,Fmotion is co-sponsored by Liverpool
OL,15,FLabour MPs Kim Johnson and Paula
OL,16,FBarker.
