OL,3,CMPs demand Hillsborough Law is
OL,4,Cdelivered 'in full and without delay'
OL,6,FOfficially named the Public Authority
OL,7,F(Accountability) Bill, the legislation
OL,8,Fseeks to end the culture of state
OL,9,Fcover-ups ` seen in scandals like
OL,10,FHillsborough and the infected blood
OL,11,Finquiry ` by creating a legal duty of
OL,12,Fcandour for public officials and
OL,13,Fauthorities, enforceable by criminal
OL,14,Fsanctions.
OL,16,FIt also aims to ensure bereaved
OL,17,Ffamilies receive equal legal
OL,18,Frepresentation.
