OL,6,FFirst introduced to Parliament in 2017
OL,7,Fby Andy Burnham, the bill was
OL,8,Foriginally drafted by lawyers who
OL,9,Frepresented Hillsborough families
OL,10,Fduring the inquests and is endorsed by
OL,11,Ffamilies and survivors of
OL,12,FHillsborough, as well as campaigners
OL,13,Ffrom other state-related scandals.
