OL,4,Cdelivered 'in full and without delay'
OL,6,FThe Early Day Motion "welcomes (Mr
OL,7,FByrne's) reintroduction of the
OL,8,FHillsborough Law" and "calls on the
OL,9,FGovernment to honour its word and the
OL,10,Fmemory of the 97 lives lost at
OL,11,FHillsborough by enacting the
OL,12,FHillsborough Law in full, without
OL,13,Fdelay."
OL,15,FByrne has expressed anger after the
OL,16,FGovernment blocked his private
OL,17,Fmembers' bill.
