OL,3,CMPs demand Hillsborough Law is
OL,4,Cdelivered 'in full and without delay'
OL,6,FHe said he was "bitterly disappointed"
OL,7,Fand, in response to reports that
OL,8,Fministers may introduce a diluted
OL,9,Fversion of the law ahead of Labour
OL,10,Fconference in Liverpool this
OL,11,FSeptember, warned: "That would not
OL,12,Fjust be a profound betrayal.
OL,14,F"Returning to Liverpool without first
OL,15,Fintroducing the real Hillsborough Law
OL,16,F` not a hollow substitute ` would be a
OL,17,Fgrave moral and political mistake."
OL,26,@nD@POUnD@fO]sD@TOUyD@cO]
