OL,6,FHe added: "But there is still time to
OL,7,Fdo the right thing. I urge the Prime
OL,8,FMinister: stand with victims of state
OL,9,Fcover-ups. Honour the 97.
OL,11,F"Fulfil your promise. Bring forward
OL,12,Fthe Hillsborough Law before you return
OL,13,Fto Liverpool in September."
OL,15,FWhen questioned on the issue at the
OL,16,FPrime Minister's Questions by
OL,17,FLiverpool Riverside MP Kim Johnson,
OL,18,FKeir Starmer said: "I just want to
OL,19,Ftake the time to get (the Hillsborough
OL,20,FLaw) right and then put it before the
OL,21,FHouse."
